## 🏗️ Project: **Vici-Monitor-Medalert-Pro**

A **professional-grade, call center operations intelligence platform** built for **Vicidial** (a widely-used open-source VoIP call center dialer). It's structured as a monorepo with 4 packages that form a full real-time data pipeline.

